org.gridgain.grid
Interface GridEnterpriseLicense

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable
public interface GridEnterpriseLicense
extends Serializable

GridGain Enterprise license descriptor. GridGain license is available for information purposes and is checked automatically by GridGain software.

Not that this license is for Enterprise Edition and available only in Enterprise Edition of GridGain. License descriptor can be obtains by calling Grid.license() method.
